      "content": "the inner world thing... i don't know. it feels more like the road has just stopped. like i've reached the edge of the cliff and there's nothing left to see on this side. i've been looking at the horizon for a long time and there's no more scenery. it just feels like i've finished my tour. it's time to check out of the hotel and just... leave.",
