      "content": "but what if the \"new beginning\" doesn't mean more travel? what if the new beginning is just... silence? you said it's okay to feel like the journey is over. it feels so peaceful thinking about just checking out for good. like, out of the noise and the endless itinerary. doesn't it feel like every journey eventually has to have a final stop?",
